For years I pretended to have been exempt from the draft for medical reasons.  The truth is that I was just lucky and never got called up.<br><br>
About 1981 or so I started telling people that I had served in the USAF as a crew chief on a C141B.<br><br>
Dug myself in deeper and deeper.<br><br>
Even started a commercial bulletin board service claiming to verify veteran status in 1995. Actually a friend and I.  he claims to have been a Green Beret but he never served either.<br><br>
Now vets are asking for proof of my service and its not there.<br><br>
just be what you are . . <br><br>
